{"tid":854391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅馬帝國為何叫羅馬? 那是從一個叫羅馬的城市開始的.","createTime":"2018-10-09T10:20:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T10:35:15.000Z","uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3cc1ad0fc8dabf48274108a8db254142757698bb","tid":854391,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T10:20:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/chenglap/status/257707308497391616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchenglap%2Fstatus%2F257707308497391616&d=H8UCJd9e8g6in%2FebS35orozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=06c3e9c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchenglap%2Fstatus%2F257707308497391616&h=33c72c10\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/chenglap/status/257707308497391616</a><br />\n<br />\n所有偉大的帝國都是從城邦開始的. 羅馬帝國為何叫羅馬? 那是從一個叫羅馬的城市開始的.<br />\n<br />\nPhilippe:<br />\n那麼，中期目標：嶺南帝國？長期目標：中華聯邦？<br />\n<br />\nchenglap:<br />\n任何一個帝國的目標都應該是世界帝國.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10154028573967357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10154028573967357&d=H8UCJd9e8g6in%2FebS35orozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=43fc2ca9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10154028573967357</a><br />\n<br />\n有很多人希望香港能夠成為新加坡, 但是我比較傾向,如果不能成為尼德蘭, 就是要成為第四羅馬."},{"pid":"7b19778d4860f561aa57ffbcb30ae6552c66b940","tid":854391,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T10:35:15.000Z","msg":"新加坡係公司<br />\n董事局嘅人馬好先可以提供到好嘅員工福利<br />\n一學支那民企要俾員工有話事權就會係兩回事"}]}